column1: IF ccr_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thaldo_d is MF 0 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 2 AND ccr_b_cortol_d is MF 2 AND ccr_sa_dihydrotest_d is MF 2 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
IF ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 1 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_the_d is MF 1 AND ccr_dha_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_pt_one_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
